Sasha nods slowly. "Jordan always said they were 'just organized.' 'Just practical.' 'Just trying to help.'"

{cards[1].reversed ? "\"Reversed — the reveal is happening now. You're seeing the frame for what it is.\"" | "\"Helpfulness that makes you smaller isn't help.\""}

"No. It's not."

+ [Let the words land] -> Sasha.Session2.Position2.End

:: Sasha.Session2.P2.Tower.Okay
