"This card represents sudden change and upheaval," you say. "Something foundational is shifting in your life."

"*Shifting.*" Sasha repeats the word with a slight edge. "It's not shifting. It's — everything I thought was true about my relationship turns out to be—"

They stop. They're doing your job for you, and you both know it.

+ [Let the words land] -> Sasha.Session2.Position2.End

:: Sasha.Session2.P2.Tower.Bad
