    "You do. And the fact that your trajectory *points there* — that's not nothing."
@endif

Sasha presses their palms to their eyes. Not crying — just *holding.* Holding the weight of the idea that there might be something on the other side of all this that doesn't hurt.

"I want that," they say. "I want to pour for myself. I've forgotten what that even means, but I want it."

+ [Let the wanting be enough for now] -> Sasha.Session2.Position3.End

:: Sasha.Session2.P3.Star.ExcellentAnalytical
